ComicInfo.Summary:
One Last Job: A bounty hunter enjoys what might be his last chase.
The Lords Of Misrule [Part 1]: A woman's arachnophobia causes a tragedy.
Nicky Nicky Nine Doors [Part 2]: Mr. Lint and Trout set out to recover one of Trout's suppressed memories.
Hectic Planet [Part 3]: Elsie is mad at her ex-boyfriend but then finds out he's dead.
Gather Ye Rosebuds: A mother dreams of her best friend.
